                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7414" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1169</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2078 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享做芯，点燃S集团数智新未来</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shared core making ignites S Group&#39;s digital intelligence new future</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵晓铃，李永红，孙晶慧，段春晓，潘秋蔚，唐飞宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">S集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务共享；应收账款业务流程；流程优化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial sharing, accounts receivable business process, process optimization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务共享中心的建立驱动了组织流程再造，推动了企业创新。应收账款业务一直以来都是企业财务共享服务中心的核心业务，尤其是对于大型制造业来说更为重要。S集团在实施财务共享模式后重新梳理了应收账款业务流程，统一了业务核算标准，实现了财务核算共享，但是作为典型的大批量离散型制造企业，S集团的应收账款业务流程在实施财务共享模式后仍然存在操作冗余、效率不高等问题。如何解决S集团实施财务共享模式后应收账款业务流程中仍然存在的问题，帮助包括S集团在内的企业有效发现大批量离散型制造企业实施财务共享后应收账款业务流程的优化措施是现实中亟待解决的问题。通过本案例帮助学生理解和掌握财务共享的相关理论及分析方法，最终实现引领学生了解财务共享服务中心建设流程以及搭建过程中的关键要点并了解各关键点之间的内在联系；带领学生对S集团财务共享服务中心的搭建过程，遇到的难点以及对财务业务流程再造的细节进行研究；帮助学生针对财务业务流程中的应收账款业务流程的现状进行具体分析，梳理存在问题并提出优化措施；分析未来财务共享中心应着重从哪些方面进行升级完善的教学目标。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The establishment of a financial sharing center has driven organizational process reengineering and promoted enterprise innovation. Accounts receivable business has always been the core business of enterprise financial shared service centers, especially for large manufacturing industries. After implementing the financial sharing model, S Group has reorganized its accounts receivable business process, unified business accounting standards, and achieved financial accounting sharing. However, as a typical large-scale discrete manufacturing enterprise, S Group&#39;s accounts receivable business process still faces problems of operational redundancy and low efficiency after implementing the financial sharing model. How to solve the problems that still exist in the accounts receivable business process after the implementation of financial sharing mode in S Group, and help enterprises including S Group effectively discover optimization measures for the accounts receivable business process after the implementation of financial sharing in large-scale discrete manufacturing enterprises is an urgent problem to be solved in reality. Through this case study, we aim to help students understand and master the relevant theories and analytical methods of financial sharing, ultimately leading them to understand the construction process and key points of the financial sharing service center, as well as the internal connections between each key point; Lead students to study the process of building the S Group Financial Shared Service Center, the difficulties encountered, and the details of financial business process reengineering; Assist students in conducting specific analysis of the current situation of accounts receivable business processes in financial business processes, identifying existing problems, and proposing optimization measures; Analyze the teaching objectives of upgrading and improving the financial sharing center in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务共享》、《会计信息系统》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务共享；财务共享中心；应收账款相关理论；业务流程；流程再造理论；业财融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
